<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="icon" href="/images/logo.ico" type="image/x-icon">
  <title>ManMode</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css1/home.css">
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">


  <style>

@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');


.about-section {
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.6;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    overflow-x: hidden;
}


.about-section h1.display-4 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.about-section h2.h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #2c3e50;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.about-section .h5 {
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #34495e;
}

.about-section .lead {
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
}


.about-section p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #555;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}


.about-section .card {
    transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.3s ease-in-out;
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
}

.about-section .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) !important;
}

.about-section .card-body {
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
}


.about-section .fas {
    color: #3498db;
}

.about-section .card .fas {
    transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
}

.about-section .card:hover .fas {
    transform: scale(1.1);
}


.about-section .bg-light {
    background-color: #f8f9fa !important;
    border-radius: 15px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
}

.about-section .list-unstyled li {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
}

.about-section .list-unstyled li i {
    margin-right: 10px;
    color: #2ecc71;
}


@keyframes fadeIn {
    from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
    }
}

.about-section .row > div {
    animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out forwards;
}


@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-section h1.display-4 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
    
    .about-section .lead {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    
    .about-section p {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    
    .about-section .card-body {
        padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
    }
}

.text-primary {
    color: #3498db !important;
}

.about-section a {
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
}

.about-section a:hover {
    color: #2980b9;
}

.section-padding {
    padding: 6rem 0;
}

.mb-custom {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
}
  </style>
</head>


<body>


  <%- include('./common-ele/nav') %>


  <section class="about-section py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12 text-center mb-4">
          <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">Welcome to ManMode</h1>
          <p class="lead">Elevating Men's Fashion, One Style at a Time</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <h2 class="h3 mb-3">Our Story</h2>
          <p>At ManMode, we believe that every man deserves to look and feel his absolute best. Founded with a passion for premium menswear, we've curated an exclusive collection of the world's finest brands under one roof. Our journey began with a simple vision: to make sophisticated men's fashion accessible, enjoyable, and effortless.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <h2 class="h3 mb-3">The ManMode Difference</h2>
          <p>What sets us apart is our unwavering commitment to quality and authenticity. Every piece in our collection is carefully selected from renowned international brands, ensuring you receive nothing but the finest in men's fashion. From casual wear to formal attire, we provide a comprehensive range that caters to the modern man's diverse lifestyle needs.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col-md-12 mt-4">
          <h2 class="h3 mb-3">Our Promise</h2>
          <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body text-center">
                  <i class="fas fa-check-circle fa-2x mb-3 text-primary"></i>
                  <h3 class="h5">Authentic Brands</h3>
                  <p>We partner directly with premium brands to ensure 100% authenticity of every product.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body text-center">
                  <i class="fas fa-star fa-2x mb-3 text-primary"></i>
                  <h3 class="h5">Premium Quality</h3>
                  <p>Each item in our collection meets the highest standards of quality and craftsmanship.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body text-center">
                  <i class="fas fa-heart fa-2x mb-3 text-primary"></i>
                  <h3 class="h5">Customer First</h3>
                  <p>We're committed to providing an exceptional shopping experience with personalized service.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col-md-12 mt-5">
          <div class="bg-light p-4 rounded">
            <h2 class="h3 mb-3">Why Choose ManMode?</h2>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                  <li><i class="fas fa-check text-primary me-2"></i>Exclusive collection of premium brands</li>
                  <li><i class="fas fa-check text-primary me-2"></i>Expert style guidance</li>
                  <li><i class="fas fa-check text-primary me-2"></i>Secure shopping experience</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                  <li><i class="fas fa-check text-primary me-2"></i>Regular new arrivals</li>
                  <li><i class="fas fa-check text-primary me-2"></i>Competitive prices</li>
                  <li><i class="fas fa-check text-primary me-2"></i>Hassle-free returns</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include('./common-ele/footer') %>
<script src="/js/nav.js"></script>

</body>

</html>